        "parameters": {
          "content": "## Setup obrigatório\n\n**Credencial Supabase API**\nSettings > Credentials > Add > Supabase API\n- Host: https://oezifbbcnqfpjakyrohh.supabase.co\n- Service Role Secret: sua service_role key\n\nVincule nos nós:\n- Download CSV do Storage\n- Upsert no Supabase\n\n**Payload do webhook (POST):**\n{\n  file_path: <caminho no bucket, ex: uuid/empresa/arquivo.csv>,\n  table: minha_tabela,\n  on_conflict: id\n}",
          "height": 340,
          "width": 500,
          "color": 4
        },
